comments: Caldwell-Pope (DEN) is moving alongside McDaniels' (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during McDaniels' drive to the basket.
Olynyk (TOR) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Barrett (TOR) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the ball is deflected by Agbaji (TOR).  Once Murray (DEN) regains possession, Barrett fully exits the lane within three seconds.
Jokic (DEN) is already in Agbaji's (TOR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Barrett (TOR) places his hands against Gordon's (DEN) back and marginal contact occurs as Barrett releases away to pursue the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) contests Barrett's (TOR) shot attempt, and the contact after the release is marginal.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) and McDaniels (TOR) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) is already in Olynyk's (TOR) path and is firming up over his right foot when contact occurs.
Murray (DEN) jumps alongside Barrett's (TOR) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Agbaji (TOR) brushes Jokic's (DEN) arm as he secures possession, and the contact is marginal.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) establishes himself in Olynyk's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Olynyk (TOR) briefly places his forearm to Jokic's (DEN) front and Olynyk immediately removes his hand as marginal contact occurs.
Agbaji (TOR) jumps from point A to point B and initiates contact with Porter Jr. (DEN) that affects his shot near the rim.
Gordon (DEN) brushes Barrett's (TOR) arm as marginal contact occurs as Gordon retreats his arm into a vertical position.
